experiment heatncool
instrument VHF
start 2013 11 27 1400
end 2013 11 27 1800
status R
description Determining the D-region heating and cooling rates in a sub-millisecond resolution
contact Antti Kero
email antti.kero@sgo.fi
operator Antti Kero
submitter Antti Kero
resources FI(14)
notes
To measure the D-region heating and cooling rates in a sub-millisecond
resolution by superposing a sufficient number of short heater on/off modulations
together. Raw data sampling makes the superposition possible.
